{"article_id":"cq0ybu8NQFwdEPx7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"When the lawyer for the former campaign manager of President Donald Trump attacked the money laundering charge","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"brought against his client","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"as flimsy ,","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"some legal experts say","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"he may have pinpointed a potential weakness in the indictment by U.S. special counsel Robert Mueller .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"Paul Manafort and his associate Rick Gates both pleaded not guilty on Monday to charges","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"that they failed to disclose","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"they were lobbying for pro-Russia former Ukrainian President Viktor Yanukovich between 2006 and 2015","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"and laundered tens of millions of dollars","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"by funneling the money through dozens of companies , partnerships and bank accounts .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"In a court filing on Thursday , Manafort defense lawyer Kevin Downing said","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"the money laundering count ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"the most serious","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"facing his client with a 20-year maximum sentence ,","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"was based on a \" tenuous legal theory \"","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"tying it to his failure","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"to register as a foreign agent of the former Ukrainian leader .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"Downing did not respond to a request for comment .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Mueller spokesman Peter Carr declined to comment .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"The language of the filing and defiant statements","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"Downing made outside the courthouse","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"following Manafort ' s arraignment on Monday","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"suggest","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"the lawyer is planning an aggressive defense of the charges , the first","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"to be made public from Mueller ' s probe into Russian interference in the 2016 presidential election .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"The Kremlin has denied meddling","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"and Trump has said","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"there was no collusion .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Neither Trump nor his campaign was mentioned in the indictments","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"issued on Monday .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Downing will also be seeking to suppress evidence","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"he said","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"was improperly obtained by search warrant ,","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"according to an additional filing on Friday .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Manafort ' s Virginia home was raided by Federal Bureau of Investigation agents over the summer .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"The money laundering statute targets financial transactions","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"involving the proceeds of \" specified unlawful activity. \"","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"According to the Manafort indictment ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"the unlawful activity was his violation of the U.S. Foreign Agent Registration Act","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"( FARA ) .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"Though the money laundering statute includes FARA violations ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Seattle tax lawyer John Colvin said","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"the charge against Manafort was not as straightforward as most other cases .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"\" It doesn ' t fit the normal paradigm \" of money-laundering cases","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"involving criminal activity like drug trafficking ,","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"Colvin said .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"\" It seems like a stretch to me . \"","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Downing said in his Thursday filing","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that only six prosecutions have been brought","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"for violating FARA","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"in the last 50 years ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"producing only one conviction .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"By pointing out the lack of previous FARA prosecutions ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"former federal prosecutor Mark Lee , now a white-collar defense lawyer in Philadelphia , said","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"Downing was likely trying to suggest","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"Manafort may not even have known","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"he was violating the law .","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"The section","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"cited by Mueller","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"requires the FARA violation to be \" knowing and willful . \"","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"Successfully casting doubt","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"on whether Manafort intentionally violated FARA","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"could knock out the money laundering charge ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"Lee said .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"\" If you don ' t have a ( specific unlawful activity ) ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"you can ' t by definition have a laundering , \"","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"said Lee .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"Former federal prosecutor Michael Padula , now a Miami defense lawyer , said","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"parts of the money laundering statute also require funds","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"to \" promote \" an ongoing criminal enterprise .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"That may be hard to show in the Manafort case ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"where the proceeds went to purchase real estate , expensive suits and Range Rovers for the conspirator ' s personal use .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"But other lawyers said","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"they doubted","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"defense arguments","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"regarding FARA","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"would gain much traction .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"\" The idea","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"that somebody of Mr. Manafort ' s background and sophistication would not understand","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"that ,","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"if he did what he is alleged to have done ,","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"he would be required to file as an agent of a foreign government ,","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"is ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"I think ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"laughable , \"","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"said Chicago lawyer and former federal prosecutor Patrick Cotter .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Several lawyers noted","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"that ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"even without the money laundering counts ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Mueller had strong charges","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"based on the failure of Manafort and Gates to report their overseas accounts to the Internal Revenue Service","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"and that the entirety of the case appeared to be backed by strong documentary evidence .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"They also pointed out","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"that Mueller could add more charges at a later date .","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"\" It ' s an argument , not a get out of jail free card , \"","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"said Padula of Downing ' s money laundering defense .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"\" He ' s still got a tough road ahead of him . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":0,"right":194,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":194,"left":102,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":100,"right":101,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":193,"left":182,"right":192,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":182,"left":115,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":106,